#### JavascriptгғўгӮёгғҘгғјгғ«

`build-clean.mjs`гғ»`build-copy.mjs`гғ»`build-css.mjs`гғ•гӮЎгӮӨгғ«гӮ’дҪңгӮҠгҒҫгҒҷгҖӮ

build-clean.mjsгҒЁbuild-copy.mjsгҒҜгҒ“гҒ®гғ‘гғғгӮұгғјгӮёгҒ«зӣҙжҺҘй–ўдҝӮгҒҷгӮӢгӮӮгҒ®гҒ§гҒҜгҒӘгҒ„гҒҹгӮҒиӘ¬жҳҺгӮ’зңҒз•ҘгҒ—гҒҫгҒҷгҖӮ


##### иӘӯгҒҝиҫјгҒҝеҮҰзҗҶ

еҗ„зЁ®гғ‘гғғгӮұгғјгӮёгӮ’иӘӯгҒҝиҫјгҒҝгҒҫгҒҷгҖӮ

```javascript
// Files
import fs from 'node:fs'
import { glob } from 'glob'
import path from 'node:path'

// SCSS
import * as dartSass from 'sass'

// PostCSS
import postcss from 'postcss'
import autoprefixer from 'autoprefixer'
import csso from 'postcss-csso'
import { enumSpreader } from 'postcss-enumerates-in-line'
```


##### гӮҝгӮ№гӮҜеҮҰзҗҶ

```javascript
const task = async () => {
  const files = await glob('src/css/**/!(_)*.scss', {
    ignore: 'node_modules/**',
  })

  files.forEach(file => {
    const distPath = path.dirname(file).replace(/^src/, 'dist') + path.sep + path.basename(file).replace(/\.scss$/, '.css')

    let body = fs.readFileSync(file, {
      encoding: 'utf-8',
    })

    body = dartSass.compile(file).css.replace(/[\t\r\n\s]+/g, ' ')

    postcss([
      enumSpreader({}),
      autoprefixer(),
      csso(),
    ])
    .process(body, {from: file, to: distPath})
    .then(res => {
      fs.writeFileSync(res.opts.to, res.css)
    })
  })
}

task()
```

PostCSSеҮҰзҗҶгҒ®й…ҚеҲ—гҒ®дёӯгҒ«гҖҒ`enumSpreader({})`й–ўж•°гӮ’е·®гҒ—иҫјгҒҝгҒҫгҒҷгҖӮ

